<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Help Page</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon_io/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    {{>header}}
    <main>
      <h3 class="title">{{title}}</h3>
      <div class="container mt-5" style="text-align: justify;">
        <ol class="p-4">
          <li class="mb-3">Enter any location in the search box. For example suppose I want to know the weather details of Kolkta. Then in the search box I will provide Kolkata</li>
          <li class="mb-3">After that click on the search button</li>
          <li class="mb-3">Below in the table you will see the weather details for the location.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </main>
    {{>footer}}
  </body>
</html>

